prospects.name: Isaac Reback
prospects.first_line: Isaac, noticed sweetgreen's expanding into Ohio with multiple locations planned—coordinating hiring and onboarding across new markets must be intense.
prospects.evidence_quote: Sweetgreen's first Ohio location is opening in 2024! While we are fully staffed for our first location, we have exciting plans for further Columbus expansion in 2025 and beyond.

prospects.name: Tiffany Porter
prospects.first_line: Tiffany, saw PCRK just acquired 36 more Massage Envy locations—managing operations across that many new sites sounds challenging.
